libgooglepinyin
------------------------------------------
Fork from google pinyin on android

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libgooglepinyin-devel-0.1.2-1bl1
  libgooglepinyin0-0.1.2-1bl1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://code.google.com/archive/p/libgooglepinyin/

Canonical download:
  https://storage.googleapis.com/google-code-archive-downloads/v2/code.google.com/libgooglepinyin/libgooglepinyin-0.1.2.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libgooglepinyin-0.1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libgooglepinyin-0.1.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libgooglepinyin-0.1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgooglepinyin-0.1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgooglepinyin0-0.1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgooglepinyin-devel-0.1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgooglepinyin-data-0.1.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libgooglepinyin)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libgooglepinyin.README

(libgooglepinyin0)
  /usr/bin/cyggooglepinyin-0.dll

(libgooglepinyin-devel)
